Now I want to propose an additional experiment.

00:01:27.549 --> 00:01:31.749
What if instead of tethering the ping pong
ball to the base of this beaker, I just got

00:01:31.749 --> 00:01:36.869
a free ping pong ball and submerged it with
my finger, just barely under the surface of

00:01:36.869 --> 00:01:37.870
the water?

00:01:37.870 --> 00:01:42.009
In that case, what do you think would happen
when the scale was allowed to rotate?

